Yeah. GOod day. AND, we were trying to throw our phones in cool ways and catch them, and lol, mine flew across the room. Kyle's did later. =P And, WE STARTED SINGING STREETLIGHT THEN THOSE D-BAGS COPIED. Me and Kyle, we OGS. =P Bitch.
